cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is about text classification using machine learning algorithms and active learning. The paper discusses the use of different machine learning algorithms and their performance on different datasets. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of forecasting models, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval (IR) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, which are relevant to the sub-categories of cs.IR and cs.AI. Finally, the paper discusses the use of data annotation and the cost of annotation, which is relevant to the sub-category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
